Package gw.api.team

Interface TeamModel

public interface TeamModel
Basic interface common to all subclasses of TeamModel. Primary type to be passed around in application-specific PCF files. Sub-interface off of this to define appplication-specific flags and functionality, then subclass off the corresponding class and implement that interface on the application side.
